 not like this advice, because it is very expensive to buy nickel at $100,0=
00 a ton, and if you buy it back now you will have lost a lot of money on y=
our short bet. =E2=80=9CNo thank you,=E2=80=9D you might=C2=A0reply. =E2=80=
