 0;">Your brokers will not like this answer, because, you know, that=E2=80=
=99s not how this works! Sure yes if the price goes down you will be happie=
r to cover your short, but the price went=C2=A0<em>up</em>, and you need to=
 cover your short=C2=A0<em>now</em>. =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99ll wait until the s=
hort squeeze ends to cover my short=E2=80=9D just fundamentally misundersta=
nds short squeezes.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Unless you are the worl=
d=E2=80=99s biggest nickel producer and have a short position so enormous t=
hat it endangers the solvency of a bunch of brokers, in which case, sure, w=
